<p></p>



<p><strong>Polygon:</strong> A polygon is a two dimensional shape with at l=
east three sides, where the sides are all straight lines.</p>



<p></p>



<p><strong>Regular &amp; irregular polygons:</strong></p>



<p></p>



<p>A regular polygon is where all angles are equal size and all sides are e=
qual length, such as a square.</p>



<p></p>



<p>An irregular polygon is where all angles are not equal size and/or all s=
ides are not equal length, such as a trapezoid.</p>



<p></p>



